entry.title: AP RGUKT IIIT Admission 2023-24 Apply 6-Year B.Tech Course from June 4
entry.summary: Rajiv Gandhi University of Knowledge Technology Andhra Pradesh (RGUKT AP) will Release admission Notification for AP IIIT Admissions 2023-24 on June 03, 2023. Admissions to 6-year Integrated B.Tech Courses will be taken on the basis of 10th Class Marks. There are four campuses of IIIT AP located in Nuzvid, Idupulayapaya, Srikakulam and Ongole.
